02:22:22,700 --> 02:22:28,100
- A God damn hollow hole.
- You're a nut.

1497
02:22:28,900 --> 02:22:35,100
Hey... guess which one of Mamie's charmers
I picked to bless me with her woman's love.

1498
02:22:35,100 --> 02:22:39,700
