1550
02:26:59,900 --> 02:27:02,900
Cured her blues, a hell of a good time.

1551
02:27:03,900 --> 02:27:06,900
You should have stuck around with me kid.

1552
02:27:06,900 --> 02:27:12,200
Taken your mind off your troubles.
