1579
02:29:23,000 --> 02:29:24,100
God!

1580
02:29:26,400 --> 02:29:31,700
I'd never believe before that anyone but whores took dope.

1581
02:29:33,100 --> 02:29:34,800
Stop it Jamie.

1582
02:29:41,100 --> 02:29:44,300
